@startuml

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam ArrowColor #2C3E50
skinparam ArrowThickness 2
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #2C3E50
skinparam RectangleBackgroundColor #EBF5FB
skinparam RectangleFontSize 14
skinparam NoteBorderColor #7F8C8D
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FDFEFE
skinparam NoteFontSize 11

title Uses Relation: Functional Dependency for Correctness

rectangle "**Module A**\n(Using Module)" as A #D5E8D4 {
}

rectangle "**Module B**\n(Used Module)" as B #DAE8FC {
}

A -right--> B : <<uses>>\nA requires B's correct\nbehavior to function

note bottom of A
  **Dependent**
  Cannot satisfy its own
  requirements without B
end note

note bottom of B
  **Depended-upon**
  Provides capability
  that A requires
end note

note as N1
  **Defining Criterion**
  A //uses// B if and only if:
  correctness of A depends on
  a correct implementation of B
end note
@enduml
